umreviews/beauty-ruin-20140603 |title=Bob Mould 'Beauty & Ruin' Album Review |publisher=[[Rolling Stone]] |accessdate=December 4, 2017}}</ref>\n}}\nUpon its release, ''Beauty & Ruin'' was met with positive reviews. At [[Metacritic]], which assigns a [[weighted mean]] rating out of 100 to reviews from mainstream critics, the album received an average score of 76, which indicates \"generally favourable reviews\".<ref name=MC>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/beauty-ruin/bob-mould |title=Beauty & Ruin Reviews |publisher=Metacritic |date=2014-05-30 |accessdate=2014-06-03}}</ref> Also, on Alternativenation.net, the album was met with positive reviews of 7/10 (or 3.5/5 Stars).<ref name=AltNation/>\n\n==Charts==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Chart (2014)\n! Peak<br />position\n|-\n|[[UK Albums Chart]]<ref name=OCC>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/4683/bob-mould/ | title=The Official Charts Company - Bob Mould| publisher=Official Charts Company| accessdate=2015-08-12}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|96\n|-\n|UK Alternative Albums\n|align=\"center\"|16\n|-\n|UK Rock Albums\n|align=\"center\"|8\n|-\n|US [[Billboard 200]]<ref name=\"allmusic-billboard\">{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/bob-mould-mn0000058386/awards | title=allmusic ((( Bob Mould > Awards )))| publisher=Billboard| accessdate=2015-08-12}}</ref>\n|align=\"center\"|38\n|-\n|US ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' [[Independent Albums]]<ref name=\"allmusic-billboard\"/>\n|align=\"center\"|5\n|-\n|US ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' Alternative Albums<ref name=\"allmusic-billboard\"/>\n|align=\"center\"|9\n|-\n|US ''[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]'' Top Rock Albums<ref name=\"allmusic-billboard\"/>\n|align=\"center\"|9\n|-\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Bob Mould}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Beauty and Ruin}}\n[[Category:2014 albums]]\n[[Category:Bob Mould albums]]\n[[Category:Albums produced by Bob Mould]]\n\n\n{{2010s-alt-rock-album-stub}}\n", "text_old": 